items.title: Buxton's walk-off homer lifts Twins over Toronto
items.summary: For the second consecutive night the Twins won on a walk-off, as Byron Buxton delivered a two-out homer in the tenth inning to push past the Blue Jays, 3-2, on Thursday night at Target Field.
